        "other_refer": [],
        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The OVAT screening result is determined according to the following points:</span><b></b></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 50.51194539249146%;\"><col style=\"width: 28.49829351535836%;\"><col style=\"width: 20.81911262798635%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Points</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Within the past month&hellip;</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner threatened you with a weapon?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner beaten you so badly that you had to seek medical care?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner acted like they would like to kill you?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner had no respect for your feelings?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Rarely</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Occasionally</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Frequently</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>4</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Very frequently</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p></p>",
        "facts": "<p>A &ldquo;yes&rdquo; answer to any of the first three questions or an &ldquo;occasionally&rdquo;, &ldquo;frequently&rdquo;, or &ldquo;very frequently&rdquo; answer to the last question is considered a positive screening result.</p>",
